Dialogs.Dialog: I'm having a hard time deciding a recommendation for the Library Committee books. I wonder what I should do...
Rinko

Even though I understand the logic of this, I just don't agree with it... I understand this kind of thing.

If Rinko were in this girl's shoes, I'd still agree with the last person.
Santa's memories. And then they decided on "conditions and punishments."――
What's that, I wonder what he's going to say... I'm curious～！
Just finished the 4th day. Fumi-chan came to school and got into a fight with a girl in her class.
You know, when you're in elementary school, you do cruel things like that... Rinko remembers that, too...
On the fifth day, the two men presented each other's idea of "conditions and punishments".

On Saturday, Fumi-chan took everyone to the zoo.
Imagine what it would be like to be invisible to all living things except humans...？
Where the sensei spoke about a past incident and apologized to Fumi-chan on the train on the way home...

On Sunday, they finally confronted Yuta Ichikawa...
I was surprised... really, I felt so betrayed... I can't believe even the sensei was fooled...
At the hospital, confessing to Akiyama-sensei...
Oh, not again, I cry when I remember...
